Package com.collabnet.ccf.pi.sfee.v44

Class Summary
Connection This class represents the required objects needed for a SOAP API connection.
SFEEAppHandler This class works with the ISourceForgeSoap object for the source SFEE system to get the Comment Texts entered by the users for an artifact.
SFEEAttachmentHandler This class is responsible for retrieving attachment data for an artifact from a Source SFEE repository.
SFEEConnectionFactory This is an implementation of the com.collabnet.ccf.core.eis.connection.ConnectionFactory that will be used by the ConnectionManager to create, close and check if the connection is live and the session id is not invalid.
SFEEGAHelper This is a utility class that is used to extract fields from Generic artifact, get the value of a field, etc.
SFEEReader  
SFEEToGenericArtifactConverter The artifact data from the SFEE SOAP API calls are in the ArtifactSoapDO object.
SFEETrackerHandler The tracker handler class provides support for listing and/or edit trackers and artifacts.
SFEEWriter This component is responsible for writing SFEE tracker items encoded in the generic XML artifact format back to the SFEE tracker
